name: "The Fields of Grey Poem Redeemable Ticket"
description: "The Fields of Grey Poem Redeemable Ticket" may be burned and redeemed for "The Fields of Grey Poem" on or before April 29, 2022. There are 10 Redeemable Tickets for 10 Poems. After April 29, 2022 any of the 10 remaining "The Fields of Grey Poems" that were not redeemed will be burned. "The Fields of Grey Poem" was written by DeadPanZoom.
